355        }

357        if ($this->ignoreMissingPage) {
358            $preparedDataReader = $this->prepareDataReaderByParams(null, null, $pageSize, $sort, $filters);
359            try {
360                return [$preparedDataReader, $this->getItems($preparedDataReader)];
361            } catch (InvalidPageException $exception) {
362            }
363        }
364
365        if ($this->pageNotFoundExceptionCallback !== null) {
366            ($this->pageNotFoundExceptionCallback)($exception);
367        }
368
369        throw $exception;
370    }
371
372    /**
373     * @throws PageNotFoundException
374     *
375     * @psalm-return array<array-key, array|object>
376     */
377    private function getItems(ReadableDataInterface $dataReader): array
378    {
379        $items = $dataReader->read();
380        return is_array($items) ? $items : iterator_to_array($items);
381    }
382
383    /**
384     * @param FilterInterface[] $filters
385     *
386     * @throws InvalidPageException
387     */
388    private function prepareDataReaderByParams(
389        ?string $page,
390        ?string $previousPage,
391        ?string $pageSize,
392        ?string $sort,
393        array $filters,
394    ): ReadableDataInterface {
395        $dataReader = $this->getDataReader();
396
397        if (!$dataReader instanceof PaginatorInterface) {
398            if (
399                $dataReader instanceof OffsetableDataInterface
400                && $dataReader instanceof CountableDataInterface
401                && $dataReader instanceof LimitableDataInterface
402            ) {
403                $dataReader = new OffsetPaginator($dataReader);
404            } elseif (
405                $dataReader instanceof FilterableDataInterface
406                && $dataReader instanceof SortableDataInterface
407                && $dataReader instanceof LimitableDataInterface
408            ) {
409                if ($dataReader->getSort() !== null) {
410                    $dataReader = new KeysetPaginator($dataReader);
411                } else {
412                    return $dataReader;
413                }
414            } else {
415                return $dataReader;
416            }
417        }
418
419        if ($dataReader->isPaginationRequired()) {
420            $dataReader = $dataReader->withPageSize(
421                $this->preparePageSize($pageSize) ?? $this->getDefaultPageSize()
422            );
423
424            if ($page !== null) {
425                $dataReader = $dataReader->withToken(PageToken::next($page));
426            } elseif ($previousPage !== null) {
427                $dataReader = $dataReader->withToken(PageToken::previous($previousPage));
428            }
429        }
430
431        if (!empty($sort) && $dataReader->isSortable()) {
432            $sortObject = $dataReader->getSort();
433            if ($sortObject !== null) {
434                $order = OrderHelper::stringToArray($sort);
435                if (!$this->enableMultiSort) {
436                    $order = array_slice($order, 0, 1, true);
437                }
438                $dataReader = $dataReader->withSort(
439                    $sortObject->withOrder(
440                        $this->prepareOrder($order)
441                    )
442                );
443            }
444        }
445
446        if (!empty($filters) && $dataReader->isFilterable()) {
447            $dataReader = $dataReader->withFilter(new All(...$filters));
448        }
449
450        return $dataReader;
451    }

710    public function render(): string
711    {
712        [$filters, $filterValidationResult] = $this->makeFilters();
713        [$preparedDataReader, $items] = $filters === null
714            ? [null, []]
715            : $this->prepareDataReaderAndItems($filters);
716
717        $content = trim(
718            strtr(
719                $this->layout,
720                [
721                    '{header}' => $this->renderHeader(),
722                    '{toolbar}' => $this->toolbar,
723                    '{items}' => $this->renderItems($items, $filterValidationResult, $preparedDataReader),
724                    '{summary}' => $this->renderSummary($preparedDataReader),
725                    '{pager}' => $this->renderPagination($preparedDataReader),
726                    '{pageSize}' => $this->renderPageSize($preparedDataReader),
727                ],
728            )
729        );
730
731        return $this->containerTag === null
732            ? $content
733            : Html::tag($this->containerTag, "\n" . $content . "\n", $this->containerAttributes)
734                ->encode(false)
735                ->render();
736    }
737
738    /**
739     * @psalm-return positive-int
740     */
741    protected function getDefaultPageSize(): int
742    {
743        $dataReader = $this->getDataReader();
744        $pageSize = $dataReader instanceof PaginatorInterface
745            ? $dataReader->getPageSize()
746            : $this->defaultPageSize;
747
748        if (is_int($this->pageSizeConstraint)) {
749            return $pageSize <= $this->pageSizeConstraint
750                ? $pageSize
751                : $this->pageSizeConstraint;
752        }
753
754        if (is_array($this->pageSizeConstraint)) {
755            return in_array($pageSize, $this->pageSizeConstraint, true)
756                ? $pageSize
757                : $this->pageSizeConstraint[0];
758        }
759
760        return $pageSize;
761    }

793    private function renderPagination(?ReadableDataInterface $dataReader): string
794    {
795        if (!$dataReader instanceof PaginatorInterface || !$dataReader->isPaginationRequired()) {
796            return '';
797        }
798
799        if ($this->paginationWidget === null) {
800            if ($dataReader instanceof OffsetPaginator) {
801                $widget = OffsetPagination::widget(config: $this->offsetPaginationConfig);
802            } elseif ($dataReader instanceof KeysetPaginator) {
803                $widget = KeysetPagination::widget(config: $this->keysetPaginationConfig);
804            } else {
805                return '';
806            }
807            try {
808                $widget = $widget->withPaginator($dataReader);
809            } catch (PaginatorNotSupportedException) {
810                return '';
811            }
812        } else {
813            $widget = $this->paginationWidget->withPaginator($dataReader);
814        }
815
816        if ($this->urlCreator === null) {
817            $nextUrlPattern = '#page=' . PaginationContext::URL_PLACEHOLDER;
818            $previousUrlPattern = '#previous-page=' . PaginationContext::URL_PLACEHOLDER;
819            $defaultUrl = '#';
820        } else {
821            $pageSize = $this->getPageSizeValueForUrl($dataReader);
822            $sort = $this->getSortValueForUrl($dataReader);
823            $nextUrlPattern = call_user_func_array(
824                $this->urlCreator,
825                UrlParametersFactory::create(
826                    PageToken::next(PaginationContext::URL_PLACEHOLDER),
827                    $pageSize,
828                    $sort,
829                    $this->urlConfig
830                ),
831            );
832            $previousUrlPattern = call_user_func_array(
833                $this->urlCreator,
834                UrlParametersFactory::create(
835                    PageToken::previous(PaginationContext::URL_PLACEHOLDER),
836                    $pageSize,
837                    $sort,
838                    $this->urlConfig
839                ),
840            );
841            $defaultUrl = call_user_func_array(
842                $this->urlCreator,
843                UrlParametersFactory::create(null, $pageSize, $sort, $this->urlConfig),
844            );
845        }
846
847        $context = new PaginationContext(
848            $nextUrlPattern,
849            $previousUrlPattern,
850            $defaultUrl,
851        );
852
853        return $widget->withContext($context)->render();
854    }
855
856    private function renderPageSize(?ReadableDataInterface $dataReader): string
857    {
858        if (empty($this->pageSizeTemplate) || !$dataReader instanceof PaginatorInterface) {
859            return '';
860        }
861
862        if ($this->pageSizeWidget === null) {
863            if ($this->pageSizeConstraint === false || is_int($this->pageSizeConstraint)) {
864                $widget = InputPageSize::widget();
865            } elseif (is_array($this->pageSizeConstraint)) {
866                $widget = SelectPageSize::widget();
867            } else {
868                return '';
869            }
870        } else {
871            $widget = $this->pageSizeWidget;
872        }
873
874        if ($this->urlCreator === null) {
875            $urlPattern = '#pagesize=' . PageSizeContext::URL_PLACEHOLDER;
876            $defaultUrl = '#';
877        } else {
878            $sort = $this->getSortValueForUrl($dataReader);
879            $urlPattern = call_user_func_array(
880                $this->urlCreator,
881                UrlParametersFactory::create(
882                    null,
883                    PageSizeContext::URL_PLACEHOLDER,
884                    $sort,
885                    $this->urlConfig
886                ),
887            );
888            $defaultUrl = call_user_func_array(
889                $this->urlCreator,
890                UrlParametersFactory::create(null, null, $sort, $this->urlConfig),
891            );
892        }
893
894        $context = new PageSizeContext(
895            $dataReader->getPageSize(),
896            $this->getDefaultPageSize(),
897            $this->pageSizeConstraint,
898            $urlPattern,
899            $defaultUrl,
900        );
901        $renderedWidget = $widget->withContext($context)->render();
902
903        $content = $this->translator->translate(
904            $this->pageSizeTemplate,
905            ['widget' => $renderedWidget],
906            $this->translationCategory,
907        );
908
909        return $this->pageSizeTag === null
910            ? $content
911            : Html::tag($this->pageSizeTag, $content, $this->pageSizeAttributes)->encode(false)->render();
912    }
913
914    private function renderSummary(?ReadableDataInterface $dataReader): string
915    {
916        if (empty($this->summaryTemplate) || !$dataReader instanceof OffsetPaginator) {
917            return '';
918        }
919
920        // The total number of rows available
921        $totalCount = $dataReader->getTotalItems();
922        if ($totalCount === 0) {
923            return '';
924        }
925
926        // The page number (1-based) current being displayed
927        $currentPage = $dataReader->getCurrentPage();
928
929        // The starting row number (1-based) currently being displayed
930        $begin = ($currentPage - 1) * $dataReader->getPageSize() + 1;
931
932        // The number of rows currently being displayed
933        $count = $dataReader->getCurrentPageSize();
934
935        // The ending row number (1-based) currently being displayed
936        $end = $begin + $count - 1;
937
938        // The number of pages available
